{
  "stem": "6845.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And Nick and I, we both realized, we don't want to save just ourselves, and everybody else will be killed or taken away someplace.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So the amazing thing was that same day that we already decided that next day, we shall just go to report that we want to go into the city, in the evening-- I don't know if Nick mentioned it that the farmers, who wanted to-- which was a very moving experience.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They wanted to help us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But we just took one look at each other, and we knew.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We don't want to be saved.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We just want to be with our family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And next day, we did go in with the-- we went in with a-- on the way down, we rented a horse, a horse and buggy somehow, not an ox cart.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we actually had a smile on our face from the beginning to the end because we shared it together with our family.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And once we got into the ghetto, it was very, very, very, shocking, very different.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But the fact that people were together, there was a very comforting feeling.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So we just kept thinking of the positive.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Well, look, we share it together with our family.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And whatever will happen, it's-- we shall be together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was thinking of my older brother by that time and the child-- anyway, the ghetto was a nightmare of nightmares because there was-- nobody tried to pretend, or could pretend.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody suffered from right and left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the whole atmosphere was, so, so what's next?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So next was just that they will take us away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we still didn't think they'd take us away to kill us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We just thought they'd take us away to work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We knew Germany is under lots of stress.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
